reviewText: great product and quick delivery to uk
The grands love the songs on this DVD, My granddaughter play it every morning before going to school. it makes our morning a lot easier, when she plays the dvd, no problems what so ever.
My kids love it and so do I. They get up and dance and have learned all the lyrics. Great exercise and movements while we worship. Have had it for six years and still a favorite. Bought CD too.
Great worship songs, easy to learn, kids love it! I recommend it highly, high energy, fun hand motions. Wish I could find more old vbs curriculums to use with the music.
Since this product was new six years ago, I was delighted to find a copy.  It is in excellent condition and will suit my summer program very well.
